description:
Responsibilities:

Assist CTO in business development and project preparation; coordinate with various departments on a variety of projects;
Cooperate with internal and external parties in organizing, executing and completing the project milestones;
Issue invoice, input sales record and review contract;
Keep track and maintain good relationship with contractors;
Carry out tasks assigned by CTO;
Outdoor work is required;
Handle ad hoc duties as assigned;

 Requirements:

5 years working experience, agricultural or fishery field is an advantage;
Have a passion for local agriculture development;
Strong people skill;
Proficiency in PC applications, e.g. Excel, Word Processing, Chinese word processing;
Good command of written and spoken English and Mandarin;

We offer competitive salary package to suitable candidate.  Interested parties, please send email for application form.

